air:Brand.Name: Economy Flexi
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Flexi
Flexi
air:Brand.air:Text: Enjoying the ability to change your flight dates for free, the option to cancel and refund your ticket and upgrade your flight with miles to Business Class when you book on Economy Flexi today.

Our Economy Class innovative design minimizes intrusion into your personal space even as the passenger in front reclines; while ergonomic styling of the seat further maximizes knee and legroom. It also features a headrest that can be adjusted as desired for greater support.
An easily accessible seatback-mounted handset, personal and non-intrusive reading light and in-seat power supply, are just some of the many intelligent touches designed with you in mind. (Applicable to most aircraft types)

air:Brand.Name: Business
air:Brand.air:Title: Business
Business
air:Brand.air:Text:
Upgrade to Business Class to experience:
1)Increased baggage allowance 2)Access to the Book The Cook service 3)Access to Singapore Airlines SilverKris departure lounges 4)A lie-flat bed (only on long-haul flights) and 5)Earn 25% more miles!

New Business Class (new Boeing 777-300ER): The new Business Class seat has been carefully designed and developed to ensure that each part is functionally and aesthetitcally excellent. Its combination of comfort, amenity and sohpistication has once again raised the bar for Business Class travel.
Long Haul Business Class (A380, Boeing 777-300ER and refitted 777-200ER): Our Business Class seat is one of the most spacious the world has ever seen. Each leather seat unfolds to reveal a large full flat bed, with more room to stretch, providing you a rejuvenating nights rest.
Other Business Class: Unwind in our medium haul Business Class cabin where we offer inclined flat seats exquisitively upholstered in premium leather (or conventional recliner seats with plush fabric cushions onboard some of our Boeing 777-200 aircraft). With adjustable headrest and lumbar support, you will arrive at your destination feeling completely rejuvenated.
Other benefits include: 1) Increased baggage allowance 2) Access to the Book The Cook service 3) Access to Singapore Airlines SilverKris departure lounges 4) A lie-flat bed (only on long-haul flights) and 5) Earn 25% more miles than Economy Flexi!
Get reacquainted with the joys of relaxation

air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Freedom
EF
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Economy Freedom to benefit from the Priority Check in facility

The best inflight entertainment, selection of fine international cuisine, and warm Arabian hospitality. Welcome to Etihads Economy Class.
Priority Check-in
100% of Etihad Guest miles
Free date changes
Free refund
Hand baggage x 1 bag at 7kgs
Upgrade eligibility
Neck pillows and soft fleece blankets for increased comfort on long-haul
Tasty hot meals with a choice of three main courses, with vegetarian as standard
On board Cafe offering light snacks and a choice of teas, coffees and hot chocolate
Flying Nanny on board offering parents a helping hand on long-haul
Hundreds of hours of on-demand entertainment, on 10.6" screen with noise reduction headsets
Connectivity on board: Wi-Fi and mobile services
A range of connection ports at each seat, including USB and laptop power supply
Amenity kits with socks, eyeshades, earplugs, toothbrush and toothpaste on all long-haul and overnight flights.
Complimentary luxury coach services between Dubai / Al Ain and Abu Dhabi International Airport.
US Preclearance facility at Abu Dhabi Airport to pre clear US Immigration before guests board their flight to the US
